    <title> CheckPoint: Torgue and Angular Acceleration</title>
    
      <p>A uniform rod of mass m and length d is acted upon by two forces of given magnitudes applied as shown. Point A is the midpoint of the rod; point B divides the rod in 2:1 ratio.
</p>
      <br/>
    
    <img width="961" alt="BK80" encrypturl="no" src="/static/problems/MIT/rayyan/check_points/Pictures/BK81.png"/>
